---
import Container from "../layouts/Container.astro";
import DecorImage from "./DecorImage.astro";

import prestonPencilCutout from "../assets/images/preston-pencil-cutout.png";
---

<Container bg="yellow" id="workshop" spacing="extra">
  <DecorImage src={prestonPencilCutout} width={430} height={235} />

  <div class="columns" id="introduction">
    <div class="left">
      <hgroup>
        <h2>Slowbuilt Workshop</h2>
        <p class="lead">Growth, Without Panic</p>
        <hr />
        <p class="small">A companion workshop series for the Slowbuilt book.</p>
      </hgroup>
    </div>

    <div class="right">
      <h3>What is it?</h3>
      <p>
        Slowbuilt is a four-session workshop series designed to help students,
        educators, and school communities rethink how growth, progress, and
        potential are understood. Rather than motivating through pressure or
        addressing disengagement with compliance-based fixes, Slowbuilt helps
        participants reinterpret progress accurately, recognize misalignment
        instead of failure, and regain agency without urgency.
      </p>
      <p>
        The workshop is experiential, reflective, and psychologically safe. It
        does not use diagnostic language, require public sharing, or promote
        one-size-fits-all solutions.
      </p>

      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <p>
        The series consists of up to four sessions, each lasting 75–90 minutes.
        Each session is built around an anchor activity that ties to the bigger
        ideas and reflection.
      </p>

      <ul class="links">
        <li>
          <a class="yellow" href="mailto:markgodi1980@gmail.com"
            >Contact me for more information</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Container>

<style>
  .columns {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin-block: 0 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .columns > div {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .left {
    max-width: 35rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .left {
      max-width: 25rem;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    /* font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 3rem); */
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block: 2rem 1.25rem;
  }

  hgroup p {
    font-family: var(--font-garamond);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 2px solid #ebc975;
    border-top-color: #f2ead6;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links {
      flex-direction: row;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .links li {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .links a {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.02rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    min-width: 100%;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    margin-block: auto;
    color: #244057;
    background-color: #ebc975;
    background-color: #f2ead6;
  }
  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links li {
      width: unset;
    }

    .links a {
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      min-width: 16rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .links a:hover {
    background-color: #244057;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
</style>
